Local rapper, Kwesta was in the United States Of America this week to promote his music and he stopped by at the famous Sway In The Morning studios in New York for an interview with Sway Hallow. The lyricist was interviewed about his music and he also performed a freestyle that was well-received by Americans. Kwesta follows in the footsteps of Cassper Nyovest and AKA who also featured on Sway In The Morning Last Year. Brought to you by People magazine For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.